you chase me after we had a quarrel.

113
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,830
Alright, let's not make a scene like this in the future.

114
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,480
I won't do that again.

115
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,610
I won't do that anymore.

116
