412
00:21:22,150 --> 00:21:22,850
then,

413
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,760
come with me to visit our company now.

414
00:21:25,840 --> 00:21:26,770
We have

415
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,480
