416
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:44,710
What's the occasion today?

417
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:50,790
Dad, you look like you're already drunk without even having a drink.

418
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:56,520
I got promoted.

419
00:21:58,040 --> 00:21:59,080
Promoted?

420
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:03,900
Are there any different positions in that old factory?

421
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:05,420
Not in our factory.

422
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,600
It's another company.

423
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,060
They invited me to work there as an engineer.

424
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:14,680
Dad, are you sure it's not a fraud?

425
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,660
How could you say that?

426
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,390
I have signed the contract.

427
00:22:19,520 --> 00:22:20,640
The treatment is very good there.

428
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,420
They were afraid that I didn't believe them.

429
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:26,410
They even gave me 5,000 as the guarantee deposit.

430
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:32,240
If you are available tomorrow,

431
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,920
I'll take you to see my new studio.

432
00:22:42,710 --> 00:22:43,880
Gu Hai, come here.

433
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,580
What?

434
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:51,270
